### Phase 11: Produce the Final Response

**File:** `pkg/fixtures/commands/ne_reboot.go` → `ProduceNeRebootCommandResponse()`

On success:

```go
cmds.CommandProcessingFinished(actorCtx,
    "QFX5120-48Y reboot completed. SWITCH-C restored communication with NE",
    "Port Type - FABRIC")

// Serializes NeRebootCommandResponse → wraps in CommandResponse envelope → publishes to Kafka
actorCtx.Produce(&commands.CommandResponse{
    CommandType:                          "...NeRebootCommandResponse",
    NotificationDataSpecificationVersion: 1,
    NotificationData:                     serializedResponseBytes,
})
```

This goes back out through layers ⑨ (CloudEventSerializer) and ⑩ (SinkLayer) → published to `"command-responses"` Kafka topic.

