### Bugs That Were Found and Fixed

| Bug | Symptom | Root Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Topic mismatch** | Message published but pipeline never processes it | Published to `"command-validated-requests"` but pipeline listens on `"business-events-management"` | Changed `commandRequestSubject` to `api.DefaultSubject` |
| **Empty reply on timeout** | `curl: (52) Empty reply from server` | The timeout branch in `select` didn't write any HTTP response | Added `504 Gateway Timeout` JSON response |
| **JSON field name** | `commandParameters` always empty/nil | Struct had `json:"parameters"` but curl sent `"commandParameters"` | Fixed tag to `json:"commandParameters"` |
| **Wrong sink type** | Response pipeline not working | Used `NatsSinkType` but command pipeline uses Kafka | Changed to `KafkaSinkType` |
